snippet.title: Facebook Values Profit Over Public Safety? Duh! | The Amber Ruffin Show
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

Former Facebook data scientist, Frances Haugen, testified before a Senate subcommittee. She shared many Facebook trade secrets, providing the company had plenty to hide. These revelations shocked a lot of Americans, but some of us weren’t as surprised...
